--- Pacifix / Ikoto ---

Pacifix arrives at his quarters, he transforms, and enters. He looks 
about, sighing as he sees picture of himself in Training School, 
pictures of his best friend, Crotale, pictures of friends, and his 
favorite music group. He sorts through the pictures and picks out 
one of each of him friends that isn't going. "I'll miss you guys..." He 
grabs several more memorable belongings, exits his quarters, and 
transforms into APC mode. He begins driving towards the Launch 
site for the space ship he has just deemed, "Hidden One".

------- Meanwhile --------

Azafroth and the other Ikoto observe their chosen bots with 
apparent intrest. The prepare to create the time-warp tunnel which 
they will use to send their bots to Earth. Azafroth shimmers as his 
plans unfold according to plans.
